      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah i'm in the shade now but i'm still struggling to talk properly like my tongue feels heavy and i cant really form sentences. it's probably just because im so wiped out from the sun right? i have some electrolyte powder here, should i just mix a bunch of it with water and wait it out? i dont really want to go to a hospital if i can help it.",
