      "content": "While electrolyte powder can help replenish lost salts, consuming large amounts can be overwhelming. Instead of mixing a huge dose, start with a small amount (about 500ml of water) and test how your body reacts, then gradually increase if needed. It's also essential to monitor your body's response, as excessive electrolyte intake can lead to stomach issues or other complications. If your symptoms persist or worsen, seeking medical attention would be a safer option.",
